text: Heinz Robert Mörschel (born 24 August 1997) is a Dominican-born German footballer who plays as a midfielder for KFC Uerdingen 05. ==Club career== Mörschel is a youth exponent from 1. FSV Mainz 05. He made his 3. Liga debut with Mainz 05 II on 10 August 2016 against VfL Osnabrück. In June 2018, Mörschel joined 2. Bundesliga side Holstein Kiel on a two-year contract. He then joined SC Preußen Münster on 1 July 2019.Offensivspieler Heinz Mörschel kommt von Zweitligist Holstein Kiel, scpreussen-muenster.de, 1 July 2019 In August 2020, he joined KFC Uerdingen 05 on a contract until June 2022. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:German footballers Category:Germany youth international footballers Category:1.
